quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  2,257,"ร–ebbi d Bab n wid iumnen. Issuffe$ iten id si tillas ar tafat. Imawlan n wid ijehlen, d iรดebbiten n tkerkas. Ssuff$en ten id si tafat ar tillas. Widak, d at tmes, nitni, degs ad wekkรดen."
  2,258,"Day ur twalav ara win inumren Ibรดahim $ef Mass is, acku Ifka yas ร–ebbi tagelda? Mi inna Ibรดahim: "Mass iw d win Issidiren, Ineqqen", inna d: "nek ssidire$, neqqe$". Inna Ibรดahim: "ihi, ร–ebbi Issenqaรด ed iรฎij seg ugmuv; keรงรง, ssenqeรด it id seg utaram"! Inneรชcam win ijehlen. ร–ebbi ur Inehhu yara agdud imednas."
  2,259,"Ne$ am win iรขaddan di temdint tilemt, thudd wakali. Inna: ยซamek ara d Issider ร–ebbi tagi, deffir tmeppant is?ยป In$a t ร–ebbi twinas iseggwasen, sinna, Issenker it, Inna: ยซacรชal teqqimev?ยป Inna d: ยซqqime$ ibwass, ne$ ur ibbwiv wassยป. Inna: ยซxaรฎi, teqqimev twinas iseggwasen. Muqel lqut ik akked tissit ik, ur xรปiรดen. Muqel a$yul ik. A k Nerr d assekni i medden. Muqel i$san amek ara ten Nessemlil, sinna, ad asen Nessels aksumยป. Mi ipputebbet, inna: ยซรฉรดi$ ร–ebbi Izmer i yal cciยป."